title: We Remembered the Titans
description:
Mina and ESPN's Matt Bowen look ahead to some of the best games on the Week 8 schedule including Patriots-Chargers, Titans-Colts, Steelers-Browns, and Packers-Cardinals. Plus, the tables get turned on Mina in Dinks and Dunks.
